PILOT AUTHORISATION
================================================================

As of 2026-04-15, BIZUSIZO pilot deployment is authorised in
writing by Tshwane District Health for three primary healthcare
facilities: Eersterus Community Health Centre, Skinner Clinic,
and Soshanguve Community Health Centre. Deployment at any other
facility without equivalent written authorisation falls outside
the scope of this pilot and is not sanctioned by the
maintainers.

